org.transitime.avl.calAmp

Class MiniEventReport

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.transitime.avl.calAmp.Report
      • org.transitime.avl.calAmp.MiniEventReport

  • public class MiniEventReport
extends Report
    Contains info for a CalAmp mini event report which is a simple GPS report. Documentation is at https://puls.calamp.com/wiki/LM_Direct_Reference_Guide# Mini_Event_Report_Message_.28Message_Type_10.29
    Author:
    SkiBu Smith

      • isValidGps

        public boolean isValidGps()
        Whether GPS fix is actually valid. Looks at top 4 bits of fixStatus to determine if Invalid Time, Invalid Fix, Last Known, or Historic are set. If any of those bits are set then the fix is considered invalid.
        Returns:
        true if GPS is not valid
